_sText: Here you have a new small - awp map. Small, fun and fast game play. A city, canal look with some random train and helicopter sounds to make it more interesting. Some quick data: - outdoors - 3d skybox - soundscape - 20CT spawns - 20T spawns - Spawn with full ammo Awp, Deagle > To install the map, put the cstrike folder in the download over the old one and over write. Commenting, rating and suggesting is more then welcome! Enjoy! :D
